divs: Sighting DetailsI went outside to let my doggie out in my fenced yard. After viewing the most profound moon halo and I have seen many but not like this one... The moving object caught my left eye and I watched it until it was not in sight. Within a minute or so it was gone. ( I said wait a minute I need to stop and look at this. I was in my yard looking to the East south east. I must say it has left me in thought of what it was.
